      "raw_text": "WALLA WALLA, Aug. 10.-The\ncounty fair association sustained a\nheavy loss yesterday in the destruc-\nton of the Playground barns by a\ngrass fire. Several horses valued\nat from 5000 to $500 each were\nalso burned. The loss is placed\nat $4,000. The buildings will be\nrestored in time for the fair."
